## Security Status

RLS is only enabled on `households` and `household_members`. The following 10 tables are **fully exposed** to the `anon` and `authenticated` roles вЂ” anyone with the anon key can read or modify every row:

`shopping_lists`, `shopping_list_items`, `recipes`, `recipe_ingredients`, `recipe_steps`, `expense_categories`, `category_splits`, `expenses`, `expense_splits`, `household_items`

`household_item_aliases` has RLS enabled. Before shipping, enable RLS on all remaining tables above.
